{"tid":194903,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人食完譚仔會屙肚？","createTime":"2017-04-10T09:52:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-10T10:32:17.000Z","uid":37129,"like":6,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e997078a955a262df4cbdfce035c6ffb13ba9811","tid":194903,"uid":37129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T09:52:50.000Z","msg":"有無人食完譚仔或者三哥之後都會屙肚？<br />\n<br />\n話說今日去睇中醫，佢俾藥我時就問我呢幾日有無屙肚。<br />\n<br />\n我就諗一諗話：前日食完譚仔之後有屙。<br />\n<br />\n佢就話：呢間d湯唔係咁好。<br />\n<br />\n我宜家諗返，係喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我好似真係每次食完都會屙肚。<br />\n<br />\n有無人其實都係一樣，開頭以為自己腸胃問題，原來問左個fd佢都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n會既，請正評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔會，係樓豬太廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e15edd589b9ba9a9ce13946b24149837c12fda2","tid":194903,"uid":37129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T10:05:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15d15f1955b98010ab2d6d47d82781592a4ee7be","tid":194903,"uid":78004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T10:09:20.000Z","msg":"我間中會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有幾次食完又痾又嘔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e412ba9e3bff516a7b5352633bfc0b7de61935f7","tid":194903,"uid":37129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T10:14:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我間中會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有幾次食完又痾又嘔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好符合你個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a923e3fcc5436997bb86f4ecc46aee4ca950f3a","tid":194903,"uid":85416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T10:19:50.000Z","msg":"會唔會係辣所以屙"},{"pid":"a813e011f215f6e42fc41dc26ccdf64fed37cb07","tid":194903,"uid":2950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T10:21:57.000Z","msg":"屙肚"},{"pid":"75143a6d45ca79c700b9e40d259fa206058842d3","tid":194903,"uid":94090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T10:24:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屙肚</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0dbfdf5aa2980c5b557724c186032bb4cb98878f","tid":194903,"uid":77788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T10:24:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e9810c3f7d0dc3613e1e2e8ee3bace6020370cd9","tid":194903,"uid":37129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T10:25:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>會唔會係辣所以屙</blockquote><br />\n我開頭就係以為自己食唔到辣所以食親辣都屙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但已經戒左辣好耐，前日食清湯，點知都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c89bfd4a887cbd1b0fdc9a1f875b796562781ac9","tid":194903,"uid":52066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T10:32:17.000Z","msg":"柯幾日"}]}